也因此陳昇決定息影，只偶爾客串或是演出MV對嘴畫面。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10092/3330782 |title=《專訪》 光良抱墓碑哭 陳昇演死人被觸霉頭飆罵導演 |accessdate=2019-04-14 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414071921/https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10092/3330782 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

